                           Project 02 - Boolean Arithmetic
                           -------------------------------
  

Submitted Files
---------------
README - This file.
README - This file
HalfAdder.hdl - Half-Adder chip (adds 2 bits)
FullAdder.hdl - Full-Adder chip (adds 3 bits)
Add16.hdl - 16-bit Adder chip (adds two 16-bit numbers)
Inc16.hdl - Incrementer chip
ALU.hdl - The Arithmetic Logic Unit chip
ShiftLeft.hdl - 16-bit Shift Left chip
ShiftRight.hdl - 16-bit Shift Right chip
Mul.hdl - 16-bit Multiplication chip (multiplies two 16-bit numbers) 


Remarks
-------
The chips are implemented according to the instructions
in the course book, chapter 2.
Some chip reuse in this project:
The Inc16 chip uses a single Add16 chip.
The ShiftLeft chip uses a single Add16 chip.
The ShiftRight uses a two Not16 chips,
and the Mul chip uses "long multiplication" method.